📍Prithvi Cafe, Juhu – where food meets art 🎭
Tucked inside the legendary Prithvi Theatre, this café is more than just a place to eat — it’s an experience. From cutting chai to mouthwatering amritsari kulchas, every corner here whispers creativity. Perfect for a chill evening with friends, or a solo date with your journal.✨

📸 Shot on iPhone 14 Pro
🪑 Ambience: Cozy, artsy, and full of stories
🍽️ Must try: beer bottle chaase, kulchas, Mumbai style cheesy pavbhaji... 

#SpendADayInMumbai #PrithviCafe #JuhuVibes #MumbaiCafes #CafeHoppingMumbai #HiddenGemsMumbai #ArtMeetsFood #MumbaiDiaries #ChaiLovers #TheatreCafe #WeekendInMumbai #BudgetFriendlyMumbai #CafeCultureMumbai #MumbaiEats #iPhonePhotography #tourism #tour #guide #lonelypanet #fodgasm #viralvídeos

📍Naturals Now, Juhu – The OG Scoop Spot 🍦🌴
This isn’t just dessert — it’s nostalgia in a cone. Naturals Now at Juhu is where the magic began! From their iconic Tender Coconut to seasonal gems like Mango and Sitaphal, every bite tastes like a coastal vacation.
Fresh. Fruity. Forever a classic.
✨ Bonus: Quick service, cosy seating, and the beach just a few steps away! Perfect post-sunset spot 🌅.
💸 ₹80–₹150 per scoop
🕒 Open till late
📌 Must-visit if you’re in Juhu!
